column5: A friend of mine and I are hoping to go fishing Sunday morning up at Lake simcoe and was wondering about where or if any boat rentals ate around? Please help.

Lots of them all around the lake,depends what part of the lake you're fishing. do a goole search. Look up these for a starter Virginia Beach Marina Harry' bait Bonnie boats Blue beacon marina Just to name a few
Just be carefull,where you venture out. PLAY SAFE.
I would not rent a used beer cap from Harry,s in Keswick, don't think I have ever heard a good report from someone renting from him
Haven't heard any stories about boats, but the service stinks! And for the record, Harry's not very nice!
+1 Grumpy old man, i dont know one person that likes him
